      • setUp

        public void setUp()
           throws java.lang.Exception
        Set Up creates an exercise and associate to it 3 questions, and add options and correct answers to each. Also creates a unit and a course to associate to the exercise where questions are, and students to associate to the answers. Emulates the actions that would be performed if these students answered some of the questions
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
